name: Luna DAO
description:
Turkey has one of the highest adoptions of crypto in the world yet it fails to inspire more artists, developers and students to have access to being a part of the blockchain revolution. At Luna DAO we fund guilds and projects that will help foster a brave community of native cryptonites. So far we have over 100 true believers amongst our community. Help us shed light on individuals unaware of the beauties of crypto and the convert no-coiners to true believers of the space. 

The contributors will get one NFT airdrop designed by our local artists that will allow them to partake in governance if donate more than 0.1 ETH.
